1/1 - 10000x10000 png

Unique artwork by Guillain Méjane (2007)

The successful first bidder will receive a print of the work (signed) with a blockchain-based certificate of authenticity. Original 1 on 1 of giclee printing Hahnemühle Photo Rag Ultra Smooth 305g in 25x25cm

- You must be able to contact me after winning a bid
- Only countries accepting shipments from France
- The work will be sent to you in a tube, and will not be framed.
- I will not be responsible for damage or loss in transit, and will do the best for safe transfer.
- Customs duties may apply depending on the country, in which case you will have to pay your own expenses.


[More info on the project](https://www.vagabond-des-etoiles.com/arts/house-guillain-mejane/)
